title: Bremen Bürgerschaft Elections
new-page: true
tags: event
priority: -2
view-if: (year = bremen_election_year and month >= bremen_election_month) or (year > bremen_election_year)
on-departure: month_actions += 1; bremen_election_year = bremen_election_year + 4 if bremen_snap_election_called == 0; bremen_election_year = year + 4 if bremen_snap_election_called == 1; bremen_election_month = month if bremen_snap_election_called == 1; bremen_snap_election_called = 0
set-jump: bremen_landtag_results

= Bremen Bürgerschaft Elections, [+ month : month +] [+ year +]

Bremen holds Bürgerschaft/Landtag elections. This system reuses the federal party-support system, applies Bremen party weights, combines DVP and Other before splitting off the Bremen-only Hausbesitzer Party, normalizes the result, and allocates **120** seats with D’Hondt.

- @calculate_bremen_landtag: Count the votes.

@calculate_bremen_landtag
on-arrival: bremen_government = 5 if bremen_government == undefined; bremen_leader = "Theodor Spitta" if bremen_leader == undefined; bremen_majority_cabinet = 1 if bremen_majority_cabinet == undefined
go-to: election_algorithm
set-jump: bremen_landtag_results

@bremen_landtag_results
on-arrival: {! var isBremenSnapElection = Number(Q.bremen_snap_election_called) === 1; Q.bremen_next_election_year_preview = (isBremenSnapElection ? (Number(Q.year) || 0) : (Number(Q.bremen_election_year) || Number(Q.year) || 0)) + 4; Q.bremen_next_election_month_preview = isBremenSnapElection ? Q.month : Q.bremen_election_month; if (typeof window !== 'undefined' && typeof window.calculateBremenLandtagResults === 'function') { window.calculateBremenLandtagResults(Q); } !}

= Bremen Bürgerschaft election results

Next Bremen election after this Bürgerschaft is due in **[+ bremen_next_election_month_preview : month +] [+ bremen_next_election_year_preview +]**.

Bremen Bürgerschaft seats: **[+ bremen_landtag_total_seats +] / 120**

Current Bremen government: **[+ bremen_current_government_name +]** ([+ bremen_current_government_parties +]) led by **[+ bremen_leader +]**.

Current government seats: **[+ bremen_current_government_seats +] / 120**. Status: **[+ bremen_current_government_status +]**. Majority cabinet: **[+ bremen_majority_cabinet +]**.

Current government leverage: **[+ bremen_leverage +]**.

