= Choose a Bremen coalition

A coalition is selectable if it controls at least **61** of the **120** Bürgerschaft seats. If no listed coalition has a majority, the incumbent Bremen government may continue as a minority cabinet.

- @bremen_select_sole_spd
- @bremen_select_spd_kpd
- @bremen_select_spd_ddp
- @bremen_select_spd_ddp_dvp
- @bremen_select_dvp_dnvp_ddp_hausbesitzer
- @new_bremen_elections: Call new Bremen Bürgerschaft elections.
- @root: Continue without changing the Bremen government.

@bremen_select_sole_spd
title: Sole SPD
subtitle: SPD — [+ bremen_sole_spd_coalition_seats +] / 120 — [+ bremen_sole_spd_coalition_status +]
view-if: bremen_sole_spd_coalition_selectable = 1
on-arrival: {! Q.bremen_government = 1; if (typeof window !== 'undefined' && typeof window.updateBremenCoalitionOptions === 'function') { window.updateBremenCoalitionOptions(Q); } !}
go-to: bremen_leader_selection

@bremen_select_spd_kpd
